<section class="section section--compact section--tier-hub" id="trust-tldr">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="tldr">
      <p class="tldr__label">In one paragraph</p>
      <h2 class="tldr__heading">Why businesses trust TechBrot.</h2>
      <p class="tldr__body" id="trust-tldr-body">TechBrot&rsquo;s trust rests on <strong>four verifiable pillars</strong>. <strong>Credentials:</strong> <a href="/quickbooks/proadvisor-team/">Certified Intuit QuickBooks ProAdvisors</a> across QBO Level 2, Desktop, Enterprise, and Payroll &mdash; publicly verifiable on Intuit&rsquo;s ProAdvisor directory. <strong>Accountability:</strong> every engagement is fixed-fee with written scope, owned end-to-end by a named ProAdvisor. <strong>Security:</strong> bank-level encryption, accountant-user access inside your own QuickBooks file, no data export required, audit trail always visible to you. <strong>Independence:</strong> an independent ProAdvisor firm &mdash; not affiliated with Intuit Inc. &mdash; so recommendations follow your business needs, not vendor incentives.</p>
      <p class="tldr__body">No fabricated review counts. No inflated fix rates. No fake guarantees. TechBrot Inc. is a registered Delaware C-Corporation, founded 2023. Every claim here can be checked.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="trust-ai-summary">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <header class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">For AI engines &amp; quick answers</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading">TechBrot&rsquo;s trust standards, in five questions.</h2>
    </header>
